a-401e-b296-5aaecb059310.shtml |title=周滨二叔周元兴被两次抄家后病死 其父未送殡 |accessdate=2014-03-08 |archive-date=2020-11-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118123533/http://v.ifeng.com/news/mainland/2014003/01619f14-10ca-401e-b296-5aaecb059310.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

